data.description: Gorgeous 1.5 story Village Builder 's home.  ALL BEDROOMS DOWN with fabulous split floorplan,  Beautiful HUGE Island Kitchen with Raised Panel Kitchen Cabinets and Granite Counter Tops and a HUGE kitchen island. . Spacious Family Room with stunning stone gas log fireplace.  Gorgeous Ceramic Tile in Baths & Utility Room, Beautiful Briar Grove Hardwood Flooring in Entry, Dining Room, Family Room, Kitchen and Breakfast! Gas Stub at Back Patio! 16 SEER HVAC and MORE! *THIS HOME IS A SMART HOME OPERATED BY AMAZON ALEXA!  Back Patio is screened and leads onto a GORGEOUS swimming pool and spa.  NO BACK NEIGHBORS.  Whole house GENERAC GENERATOR !!!! This home really has it all.
